title: Sabatoge Sound System - The Boto Machine Gun (2009)
description:
A new side project from Pepper's Kaleo (One of the lead vocalists and lead guitarist), Dub (Pepper's sound man), and featuring Splinta (LAW Records Artist).

These seventeen tracks have a decidedly laid back, rural island feel. All at once dirty, sexy, and lethal, "The Boto Machine Gun" is inspired by soul, Hawaiian, dub, hip-hop, and the Jamaican soundclash scene

Enjoy!

Buy it if you like it, support good music! Attend shows!!

Please Comment,

-Karlsbad
